    <itunes:subtitle>Steve Tiffen the CEO and President of the Tiffen Group joins Craig to discuss photographic filters and digital filter software, and lens and camera accessories for the imaging, broadcast television, and motion picture industries.  Today, the company offer</itunes:subtitle>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;Steve Tiffen the CEO and President of the Tiffen Group joins Craig to discuss photographic filters and digital filter software, and lens and camera accessories for the imaging, broadcast television, and motion picture industries.  Today, the company offers a wide range of products, which include: Tiffen&amp;reg; filters, Steadicam&amp;reg; camera stabilizing systems, Lowel&amp;reg; lighting solutions, Listec&amp;trade; teleprompters, Tiffen Dfx&amp;reg; digital filter suite, Domke&amp;reg; bags, Davis &amp;#38; Sanford&amp;reg; tripods, Zing&amp;reg; camera covers, Stroboframe&amp;reg; flash brackets, Saunders&amp;reg; professional trimmers, and Kodak Wratten&amp;reg; filters.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    <itunes:summary>Steve Tiffen the CEO and President of the Tiffen Group joins Craig to discuss photographic filters and digital filter software, and lens and camera accessories for the imaging, broadcast television, and motion picture industries.  Today, the company offers a wide range of products, which include: Tiffen® filters, Steadicam® camera stabilizing systems, Lowel® lighting solutions, Listec teleprompters, Tiffen Dfx® digital filter suite, Domke® bags, Davis &amp; Sanford® tripods, Zing® camera covers, Stroboframe® flash brackets, Saunders® professional trimmers, and Kodak Wratten® filters.</itunes:summary>
