    <description>&lt;p&gt;Christina Sanz the VP of Marketing at Parrot joins Craig on the floor of CES to discuss their line of high-tech, high-style products for the home, the vehicle and beyond. Parrot will unveil two new audio products, designed in conjunction with a world-renowned designer. The products present the best in style as well as technology. Automotive: Parrot is taking its groundbreaking ASTEROID car receiver even further at CES 2012 with new developments to the Android-powered ASTEROID platform. Also the ever popular &amp;bull; AR. Drone: The AR.Drone has taken CES by storm since it was introduced in 2010. This year is no different as Parrot will launch exciting new developments with the AR.Drone.  Immediately following this interview Craig will be joined by Robin Raskin the founder of Living in Digital Times.  They will discuss the following Expos and Conferences at 2012 CES: Silvers, Digital Health, Higher TechEd, Kids@Play, Sports &amp;#38; FitnessTech and MommyTech as LIDT looks at digital solutions throughout all of life&amp;#8217;s stages. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
